<h4 id="im-시리즈-14">IM 시리즈 14</h4>

<p>Description</p>
<ol>
  <li>무엇을 말하고싶은지 -&gt; MP
    <blockquote>
      <p>Alright, I’ll tell you what. I really love my room.<br />
Because, it’s just so big.</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
  <li>그것에 대해 어떻게 느꼈는지
    <blockquote>
      <p>I could invite anyone over and there’s absolutely no problems, right?<br />
I mean, like, honestly, I don’t really like small rooms, because…<br />
well, like I just told you, I cannot invite anyone over.<br />
You know, I always worry about, you know, are they gonna fell comfortable, blah, blah, blah</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
  <li>왜 그렇게 느꼈는지
    <blockquote>
      <p>But you know, like, because my room so big, you know, I feel confident and I feel happy inviting people over.<br />
because, you know, I know that everyone will have a good time, in a very spacious environment.</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
</ol>

<p>Habit</p>
<ol>
  <li>General MP -&gt; usually <strong>do</strong>, 감정 X
    <blockquote>
      <p>Honestly, you know, to tell you the truth, whenever I go to the bank, I always make sure to bring my wallet. with all my credential.</p>
    </blockquote>
  </li>
  <li>답변이 짧을 때 quick comparison 전략을 써보기</li>
</ol>

<p>Past experience</p>
<ol>
  <li>Past 시제를 잘 지키기</li>
  <li>클라이막스를 먼저 말하기</li>
</ol>

<p>Comparison</p>
<ol>
  <li>MP를 현재에 대해서만 간단히</li>
  <li>과거에 대해서 말하기</li>
  <li>현재에 대해 설명</li>
  <li>결론</li>
</ol>

<p>시간이 아닌 A와 B의 비교</p>
<ol>
  <li>A와 B를 던져줌</li>
  <li>A에 대해 설명</li>
  <li>B에 대해 설명</li>
  <li>결론</li>
</ol>

